title: SEI Club, a Members-Only Dating Club, Announces Expansion into Asia
text:
Submitted by admin on 10/26/2015 @ 3:55 AM Companies mentioned in this article: SEI Club 
LOS ANGELES, Oct. 26, 2015 /PRNewswire-iReach/ -- The founders of SEIClub.com , an exclusive members-only dating club for affluent and accomplished single men and women, are proud to announce the expansion of their company into Hong Kong and Singapore. To celebrate the growth of SEI Club into Asia, the company has also launched an updated website. 
Photo - http://photos.prnewswire.com/prnh/20151024/280208 
As a spokesperson for SEI Club noted, the dating club has earned a positive reputation for its exclusive and well-maintained network of elite singles. To become a member, interested people need to fill out a formal application; right now, the spokesperson said, about 25 to 30 percent of international membership applications are being accepted. 
The founders of SEI Club understand that there are many people who wish to have a meaningful relationship with another special person, but that work, family and other commitments can get in the way of getting out to meet other people. 
This knowledge inspired them to create SEI Club--to help successful single men and women who want to date to meet other people who share their goals and interests. Standard Memberships start at 1,200 USD and Private Memberships go up to 300,000 USD, the spokesperson noted. 
The SEIClub.com review section of the updated website is filling up with positive testimonials from people who are happy with their membership. Other SEIClub.com reviews posted on other websites also feature words of praise for the dating and matchmaking club. 
For example, one of the SEI Club reviews noted how the SEI Club team truly understood the man's situation, and helped him find an attractive and successful woman who he is enjoying getting to know. 
"Rest assured, our executive team meets every single male and female member in person so you always know you're being introduced to someone you'd honestly enjoy meeting, dating, and potentially forming a serious relationship with," noted the company spokesperson. 
"We protect your privacy, save your time, and weed out the unsuitable candidates so you don't have to." 
About SEI Club: 
SEI Club is the most preferred matchmaking and dating club for those accustomed to excellence. SEI Club is a positive force. Members' privacy is a cornerstone of SEI policy. The Club mission is to make life more peaceful, balanced, beautiful, and meaningful. Their goal is to find this special one for their members. Their process is effective, solid and reliable. SEI Club is an especially exclusive global network - whether people are looking to just date and see where it goes, or looking for long-term relationships, or hoping to marry and settle down, they have them covered. Learn more at: http://www.seiclub.com/
